	"You have agreed to cover for %1$s (%2$s) from %3$s to %4$s. An iCalendar file is attached so you can add it to your calendar." : "You have agreed to cover for %1$s (%2$s) from %3$s to %4$s. An iCalendar file is attached so you can add it to your kalendarz.",
